<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5363121>
    dc:description "Figs 1–5. Holotype of Sphaeridium daemonicum sp. nov. 1 – dorsal view; 2 – lateral view; 3 – ventral view; 4 – detail of head and anterior leg; 5 – elytral apex." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5363121/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5363123>
    dc:description "Figs 6–11. Sphaeridium daemonicum sp. nov. (6–10 – holotype, 11 – paratype from Tenasserim): 6 – aedeagus; 7 – apex of the median lobe; 8 – apex of paramere; 9 – protarsus (only tarsomeres 3–5 shown); 10 – lateral margin of pronotum; 11 – abdominal ventrites." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5363123/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

